'''Dorian passion fruit''' were a sweet [[Fruit/Legends|fruit]] native to [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]]. It was used to accent various dishes. [[Winslau Da'k's Jedi Master|An unknown ancient]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]], who was a prisoner to his fallen [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Winslau Da'k]], was fond of the fruit.

